{
  "stem": "27129.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was running in his same direction, and we finally joined up and we went where all the Jewish people were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took us to-- to a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] police command, [NON-ENGLISH], they call it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And over there they gathered us and they started searching.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because some people, if they have some watches or gold rings or, you know, whatever, then they started beating us up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe it was a good thing that they were beating us because I got such a bad taste for the Germans that I-- I wanted to be on the-- on the other end of the world, you know, as far as I could be from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that-- that was our idea, just to be as far as we can, not to be too close.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had only 100 zlotys, which was like $100, which was not much for the two of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at least, ans my brother had it hidden, you know, in the shoe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was scared, you know, they'll found it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was going to get a, you know, a roughing up, or they could shoot him too, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't find it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Ans we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went to the no-man's land.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, there was demarcation line which was a temporary border between the Russians and the Germans, which was done between, you know, between an agreement between-- between the Russians and the Germans, because the Russians took Eastern Poland which was Western Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, when we came into no-man's land, you know, it started snowing, and people laying on street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians didn't let us in, didn't let go farther.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we got stuck over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't have papers or anything?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You didn't need papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
